text: Bouchaib Zeroual (born 1917) is a Moroccan former sports shooter. He competed in the 50 metre rifle, three positions and 50 metre rifle, prone events at the 1960 Summer Olympics. ==References== Category:1917 births Category:Possibly living people Category:Moroccan male sport shooters Category:Olympic shooters of Morocco Category:Shooters at the 1960 Summer Olympics Category:Sportspeople from Rabat
